Q1) Create a record called Customer, which accepts id, name and bill as a component.

Create an ELC class CustomerComparator with main method.

Create a Customer array with dynamic size and dynamic array initialization using Scanner class. 

Sort the Customer object based on following criteria :

  a) By using Customer id
  b) By using Customer name
  c) By using Customer bill

Q2) Program to insert an element in the Array in the miidle of the Array.

    int[] arr = {1, 2, 3, 5, 6}; [Original Array]
    Array after insertion: [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6]

Q3) Find Pairs with a Given Sum
    Problem: Find all pairs (x, y) in the array where x + y = targetSum

     int[] arr = {2, 7, 4, 8, 3, 5, 1, 6};
     int targetSum = 9;

     Pairs with sum 9:
     (2, 7)
     (4, 5)
     (8, 1)
     (3, 6)


Q4) Find the Smallest and Largest Elements in an Array.
     int[] arr = {15, 3, 7, 22, 5, 9, 12};

     Smallest element: 3
     Largest element: 22

Q5) Find Common Elements in Two Arrays.

    int[] arr1 = {1, 3, 4, 7, 9, 10};
    int[] arr2 = {2, 3, 7, 6, 9, 12};

    Common elements: 3 7 9


